---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us | NexusGold">
    <section class="py-20 bg-primary">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="section-title mx-auto">About Aevum Nexus</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mt-8 text-lg">Discover our story, our mission behind our success.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Company Story -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
                <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Aevum Nexus was born from a shared passion. As two web developers, we were frustrated by how businesses struggled to express their identity online in a digital age. We named our company Aevum Nexus, meaning timeless connection, to craft elegant, enduring designs that empower our clients.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">What began as a small team has grown into a global digital agency. We are driven by excellence, innovation, and a deep commitment to our clientsâ€™ success. Every project we take on pushes the boundaries of creativity and quality.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Today, Aevum Nexus creates more than websites, we build lasting legacies. We stay true to our values of creativity, precision, and client satisfaction. Our mission is to shape a digital future as unique as our clients.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
                    <div class="card h-full overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-accent/30">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
                            <img 
                                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80" 
                                alt="Our team collaborating" 
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                            />
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6">
                                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent mb-4"></div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl text-white">Where Innovation Meets Elegance</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Mission & Values -->
            <div class="bg-black/80 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-24 border border-accent/20">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white mb-6">Our Mission & Values</h2>
                    <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto"></div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="p-6 bg-primary-light rounded-xl border border-accent/10 hover:border-accent/30 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Innovation</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400">We constantly push boundaries and explore new technologies to deliver cutting-edge solutions.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 bg-primary-light rounded-xl border border-accent/10 hover:border-accent/30 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Quality</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400">We never compromise on quality, ensuring every project meets our high standards of excellence.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 bg-primary-light rounded-xl border border-accent/10 hover:border-accent/30 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Collaboration</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400">We believe in the power of teamwork and partnership, working closely with our clients to achieve success.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-dark to-primary border border-accent/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white mb-6">Ready to Work With Us?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Let's collaborate to bring your vision to life with our expertise in design and development.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout> 